Academy_Award_for_Best_Picture_(1950s)	The Academy Award for Best Picture is one of the Academy Awards of Merit presented annually by the Academy of Motion Picture Arts and Sciences ( AMPAS ) to artists working in the motion picture industry .	The Academy Award for Best Picture is one of the Academy Awards .	2







Academy_Award_for_Best_Picture_(1950s)	The Academy Award for Best Picture is one of the Academy Awards of Merit presented annually by the Academy of Motion Picture Arts and Sciences ( AMPAS ) to artists working in the motion picture industry .	Also called Oscars , the Academy Awards are given to people working in the movie industry by the American Academy of Motion Picture Arts and Sciences ( AMPAS ) .	3







