Academy_Award_for_Best_Picture_(1950s)	During the annual Academy Awards ceremony , Best Picture is reserved as the final award presented and , since 1951 , is collected at the podium by the film 's producers .	The Academy Award for Best Picture is one of the Academy Awards .	0







Academy_Award_for_Best_Picture_(1950s)	During the annual Academy Awards ceremony , Best Picture is reserved as the final award presented and , since 1951 , is collected at the podium by the film 's producers .	Also called Oscars , the Academy Awards are given to people working in the movie industry by the American Academy of Motion Picture Arts and Sciences ( AMPAS ) .	0







Academy_Award_for_Best_Picture_(1950s)	During the annual Academy Awards ceremony , Best Picture is reserved as the final award presented and , since 1951 , is collected at the podium by the film 's producers .	In the list below , the winner of the award for each year from 1950 to 1959 is shown first , followed by the other nominees .	0







