Academy_Award_for_Best_Picture_(1950s)	The Academy Award for Best Motion Picture is considered the most important of the Academy Awards , as it is the final award presented , and represents all the directing , acting , music composing and writing efforts put forth for a film .	The Academy Award for Best Picture is one of the Academy Awards .	0







Academy_Award_for_Best_Picture_(1950s)	The Academy Award for Best Motion Picture is considered the most important of the Academy Awards , as it is the final award presented , and represents all the directing , acting , music composing and writing efforts put forth for a film .	Also called Oscars , the Academy Awards are given to people working in the movie industry by the American Academy of Motion Picture Arts and Sciences ( AMPAS ) .	0







