Academy_Award_for_Best_Picture_(1950s)	The next year , the Academy instituted a single award called Best Production , and decided retroactively that the award won by Wings had been the equivalent of that award , with the result that Wings is often listed as the winner of a sole Best Picture award for the first year .	The Academy Award for Best Picture is one of the Academy Awards .	0







Academy_Award_for_Best_Picture_(1950s)	The next year , the Academy instituted a single award called Best Production , and decided retroactively that the award won by Wings had been the equivalent of that award , with the result that Wings is often listed as the winner of a sole Best Picture award for the first year .	Also called Oscars , the Academy Awards are given to people working in the movie industry by the American Academy of Motion Picture Arts and Sciences ( AMPAS ) .	0







